Package sem

Contains the handling of scope for semantically analyzing input files.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Array_Descriptor
    Array_Descriptor class -- used for C- array variables.
    Descriptor
    This is an abstract class that defines entries to the hashtables it will be extended to a diverse collection of classes that will be used to describe the types and semantics of the various components of a C- program.
    Empty_Descriptor
    SEMempty class -- used to denote an empty entry in the hash table
    Formal_Descriptor
    Formal_Descriptor class -- used for C- parameters in function definition.
    Func_Descriptor
    Func_Descriptor class -- used for C- functions.
    SEMscope
    Handles scope for the semantic anaylsis of C Minus it employs a hash table to store and lookup symbols as they are created
    Variable_Descriptor
    Variable_Descriptor class -- used for C- variables.

Package sem Description

Contains the handling of scope for semantically analyzing input files.
